                        <a href="" class="author-name">James Taylor</a>
                    </div>
                    <h3>Top Best 10 Tips for Learning at Work</h3>
                    <p class="blog-excerpt">Discover proven strategies to maximize your learning potential and advance your career while balancing daily responsibilities.</p>
                    <div class="blog-footer-row">
                        <a href="" class="link2">Read More</a>
                        <span class="blog-read-time">
                            <i class="fa-regular fa-clock"></i> 5 min read
                        </span>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="blog-card-single">
                <div class="blog-img">
                    <span class="blog-category-badge">Career</span>
                    <img src="~/assets/images/blog-02-600x486.jpg" alt="Career Growth">
                </div>
                <div class="blog-text">
                    <div class="blog-meta">
                        <span>Jun 8, 2025</span>
                        <span class="dot-sep"></span>
                        <a href="" class="author-name">James Taylor</a>
                    </div>
                    <h3>Top Best 10 Tips for Learning at Work</h3>
                    <p class="blog-excerpt">Unlock new opportunities and elevate your professional skills with these expert-curated insights for modern learners.</p>
                    <div class="blog-footer-row">
                        <a href="" class="link2">Read More</a>
                        <span class="blog-read-time">
                            <i class="fa-regular fa-clock"></i> 4 min read
                        </span>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="blog-card-single">
                <div class="blog-img">
                    <span class="blog-category-badge">Technology</span>
                    <img src="~/assets/images/blog-02-600x486.jpg" alt="Tech Learning">
                </div>
                <div class="blog-text">
                    <div class="blog-meta">
                        <span>Jun 5, 2025</span>
                        <span class="dot-sep"></span>
                        <a href="" class="author-name">James Taylor</a>
                    </div>
                    <h3>Top Best 10 Tips for Learning at Work</h3>
                    <p class="blog-excerpt">Stay ahead of the curve with the latest trends in online education and technology-driven learning environments.</p>
                    <div class="blog-footer-row">
                        <a href="" class="link2">Read More</a>
                        <span class="blog-read-time">
                            <i class="fa-regular fa-clock"></i> 6 min read
                        </span>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

        </div>
    </div>
</section>
